issue.title: Parse all possible Order creation functions.
Parse all possible Order creation functions.
Ubuntu Node.js server does not handle multiple package versions as expected.
issue.body:
`ethers-contracts@2.1.3` Interface should provide signatures attached to function objects, but it appears that Node wants to use 2.1.2 which breaks `ethereum-tx-decoder`. This is unexpected since it works fine for me locally on OS X.

Rolled back live version to 44d3dc8c4871a66ac72a5cb6ecbd63c929d57a46 for now.
